{
  "stem": "26022.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So he was known as the white raven.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It didn't help anybody, anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But when the Kristallnacht came-- and this is where I said that is the silver lining-- we didn't have to worry, because he was already, A, in jail, and B, not as a Jew and not in a Jewish holding facility or anything.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was just plain in jail, among all his fellow Aryan jailmates, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So he was safe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And this was a horrible thing, this Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It got the name much later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I mean, We never realize that this was called Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And do you remember other episodes of Nazi cruelty?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not that that started with the Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, we had no phone anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We did still live in that part of the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we had taken a lawyer to see what goes on with my father.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was supposed to call the lawyer, and since we had no phone in the house anymore, I went down the street to the public phone, which was a block away and at the corner.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I made my phone call and called the lawyer, came out of this phone booth, and two brown shirts-- the SA-- two brown shirts were there and tried to arrest me because I am a spy and I have given information to-- in French-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to a foreign newspaper.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was flabbergasted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I called Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[GERMAN], please, call him back, and he'll tell you that we just spoke.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't even know French.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What-- what-- what information could I have?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There is no information to give-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nothing much happened today that's different from yesterday.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
